nodes.text: Rebellion 14: Small Victories, Part 4 is the fourteenth issue in the Star Wars: Rebellion series of comics.
Luke Skywalker and Princess Leia lead a team of Rebels to their destinies in the full-tilt conclusion to "Small Victories"!

Facing a situation of unparalleled danger deep behind enemy lines, a few surviving Rebels test their resolve as decisions made on the fly will have serious consequences for both the Alliance and the Empire. Meanwhile, Admiral Gial Ackbar calls a squad of experimental starfighters into action, but this is no simulation—if these new ships aren't up to the challenge, the Rebellion's hopes may be dashed by the Imperial fist!
The Star Destroyers in this issue are portrayed with sideway hangars as in Star Wars: Battlefront II.
